00:46:10.410 --> 00:46:13.020
to the percent of variance
because it's like people

00:46:13.020 --> 00:46:14.300
understand that more.

00:46:14.300 --> 00:46:15.620
I don't know, maybe not.

00:46:15.620 --> 00:46:17.649
Maybe people would have
preferred a correlation.

00:46:17.649 --> 00:46:19.190
But, yeah, that's
where it came from.

00:46:19.190 --> 00:46:22.590
So just directly off of
their published studies.

00:46:22.590 --> 00:46:26.440
They don't describe it
that way in their studies.

00:46:26.440 --> 00:46:28.940
AUDIENCE: What's your opinion
on strategies like drink water

00:46:28.940 --> 00:46:31.060
before, if you want
to lose weight; after,

00:46:31.060 --> 00:46:32.516
