00:55:02.420 --> 00:55:04.770
So it was their
full-grown adult weight

00:55:04.770 --> 00:55:06.926
for both sets of parents.

00:55:06.926 --> 00:55:08.000
Yeah.

00:55:08.000 --> 00:55:09.270
It's crazy.

00:55:09.270 --> 00:55:10.949
It's so cool that
